import { AppBar, Container, Toolbar, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

function Header() {
  return (
    <AppBar position='static' color='transparent'>
      <Container>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography>
            Crypto Hunter
          </Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </Container>

    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default Header
